{"title":"散步的老人","authors":["赵贵辰"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":2,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"散步的老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵贵辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割庄稼的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被庄稼一一收割了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只留下蹒跚步态　和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫的白发之雪　从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就叫做冬天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而你温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵依然是绿的　愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与土地的生机共存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拎不起锄头可拎得起目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走不远汗水可走得远经验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的脚印在路上拔节　拔节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的拐杖在四季里抽穗　抽穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地说“你好”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是用满畦的豆荚说的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说“你好”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是借儿子的劳动说的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能舍得分开呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这知己的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那小院的舒适"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陡然成为蚕茧了　你不愿做"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眠期的蚕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使青春已是谷茬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有茂盛的恋情呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与土地一起散步心里高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看庄稼炫耀生长心里高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更高兴的　是你捉回的几只蟋蟀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒在缸里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精采地演出你的过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时，也想立刻死去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好　与土地融为一体"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}